data.description: Warm & cozy updated farmhouse on large, level, well landscaped intown lot convenient to all town amenities.  Town water & sewer. Extensive decking to back & side yard. Vinyl windows. Wood burning fireplace in living room. 3 car attached garage.  Updated & spacious eat in  kitchen with JennAir commercial range and sliders to covered porch. Recently renovated 2nd floor bath. 4 bedrooms. This is a well loved home! Pre-sale home inspection report available to serious Buyers upon request.
